RABAT, Morocco, March 6, 2023/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            His Majesty King Mohammed VI sent a congratulatory message to president of the Republic of Ghana, Nana Akufo-Addo, on the occasion of his country's National Day.




                                HM the King takes this opportunity to express His determination to continue working together with the Ghanaian president
                            

In this message, the Sovereign expresses His warmest congratulations and best wishes of good health and happiness to Akufo-Addo, and of further progress and prosperity to the Ghanaian people.



HM the King takes this opportunity to express His determination to continue working together with the Ghanaian president to strengthen the fruitful cooperation and active solidarity between Morocco and Ghana and to take these relations to a new level for the benefit of both peoples and for the sake of unity, stability and progress in Africa.